or to your dad.

22
00:03:45,184 --> 00:03:47,269
I thought we were meeting him after.

23
00:03:47,436 --> 00:03:51,773
No way. He's coming, and then you
guys are going camping. Remember?

24
00:03:51,940 --> 00:03:54,651
He's gonna be late,
and then everyone will see.

25
00:03:57,196 --> 00:04:00,782
Look, he knows what time it starts.
Don't worry, he'll be there.

26
00:04:04,077 --> 00:04:06,079
-Hey, look at me.
-What?

27
00:04:06,246 --> 00:04:08,790
-You got something on your face there.
-Where?

28
00:04:08,957 --> 00:04:11,460
-Right there.
-Ma! Mom! Mom, no! Stop!

29
00:04:11,627 --> 00:04:13,712
There it is. I got it!

30
00:04:19,676 --> 00:04:22,804
-Hey, guys. How's it going?
-Hey, Ty.

31
00:04:22,971 --> 00:04:26,475
What's up?
The speech thing is at 4:00.

32
00:04:26,642 --> 00:04:29,561
I know. Come here.
You got something on your face.

33
00:04:29,728 --> 00:04:31,313
-Mom!
-What?

34
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:35,901
-Please.
-I’m sorry. Mr. Cool Guy.

35
00:04:37,236 --> 00:04:38,987
I love you.

36
00:04:42,574 --> 00:04:44,451
Have a good day.

37
00:05:39,173 --> 00:05:41,466
-Morning, Marisa.
-What's up, Cora? How my diamonds?

38
00:05:41,633 --> 00:05:45,554
-They're hanging with your rubies.
-I like the sound of that.

39
00:05:52,686 --> 00:05:56,064
