arrives today.

97
00:09:41,707 --> 00:09:43,125
He's gearing up his campaign...

98
00:09:43,292 --> 00:09:45,878
...so his suite will be doubling
as a conference centre...

99
00:09:46,044 --> 00:09:49,715
...with the liquor and coffee bars
turning over every four hours.

100
00:09:49,882 --> 00:09:54,261
And he's bringing his large dog,
so we'll need proper accoutrements.

101
00:09:54,428 --> 00:09:58,265
And finally, Mr. Newman is back
in the Sherman Suite.

102
00:09:58,432 --> 00:10:02,269
Careful, ladies, he's a full Monty.

103
00:10:05,105 --> 00:10:09,026
-I had no idea anyone was here.
-Don't worry about it, Mr. Monty.

104
00:10:09,193 --> 00:10:10,861
No big deal.

105
00:10:11,028 --> 00:10:15,032
-And I do mean no big deal.
-No big deal.

106
00:10:21,455 --> 00:10:23,790
Lavender!

107
00:10:24,458 --> 00:10:27,336
-You're very creative, Marisa.
-Thank you, ma'am.

108
00:10:27,586 --> 00:10:31,924
Since you have to leave at 3:00,
go find Lionel and have him sign off.

109
00:10:34,301 --> 00:10:38,639
-Sir, I need you to sign off on the--
-Damn!

110
00:10:38,805 --> 00:10:42,226
Oh, good Lord. Here, let me.

111
00:10:42,392 --> 00:10:44,978
-Here you go.
-Thank you.

112
00:10:45,145 --> 00:10:47,523
Oh, God. Your hand's bleeding.

113
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:52,402
Here. Squeeze tight.

114
00:10:57,658 --> 00:11:01,453
