219
00:16:46,590 --> 00:16:49,134
Being that we're sisters
in the service business...

220
00:16:49,301 --> 00:16:50,427
...and I’m in a rush...

221
00:16:50,594 --> 00:16:53,222
...I’d say you start serving
your low-end customers...

222
00:16:53,388 --> 00:16:55,349
...because that's
the reason you're here.

223
00:16:55,516 --> 00:16:58,310
Unless we're not good enough
for you to service.

224
00:16:58,727 --> 00:17:00,896
In which case,
I’m sure your manager is.

225
00:17:01,063 --> 00:17:03,273
What do you say, ladies?
Am I right or am I right?

226
00:17:03,440 --> 00:17:05,734
-You're right.
-Oh, yes.

227
00:17:09,029 --> 00:17:11,281
-Sorry, Mom.
-Baby, where were you?

228
00:17:11,448 --> 00:17:12,574
Keef, do me a favour.

229
00:17:12,741 --> 00:17:14,535
These go to the goddess
in the Park Suite.

